%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Inside%20Alaska%20Airlines%20plane%20as%20part%20blows%20off%20mid-air%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704527479000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10037%2Fproduction%2F_132219556_p0h3f2fx.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67900834%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Social%20media%20footage%20shows%20passengers%20on%20board%20the%20aircraft%20moments%20after%20it%20lost%20a%20section%20of%20its%20fuselage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-us-canada-67900834%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'That%20Infernal%20Infidel%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah'%3A%20Sour%20Notes%20on%20the%20Confluence%20of%20Cultures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06130952%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son%2C%20absent-mindedly%2C%20flashed%20a%20photograph%20on%20his%20mobile%20screen%20%E2%80%93%20a%20bearded%20Muslim%20was%20reciting%20Sanskrit%20chants.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CQuite%20some%20heavens%20would%20break%20on%20the%20heads%20of%20quite%20some%20persons%20when%20they%20see%20this%20image.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Perhaps%2C%20he%20was%20correct.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20members%20of%20the%20myopic%20Hindu%20community%20would%20have%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20dare%20an%20infidel%20utter%20our%20pure%20verse%20written%20in%20our%20%3Cem%3Eadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ebhasha%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bliterally%2C%20ancient%20language%5D%20Sanskrit%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Similarly%2C%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20would%20have%20possibly%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20dare%20a%20true%20Muslim%20recite%20a%20prayer%20reserved%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekafir%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%3F%E2%80%9D%20There%20is%20an%20alarming%20contiguity%20in%20these%20two%20sides%2C%20one%20inciting%20the%20other%2C%20and%20both%20summarily%20rejecting%20a%20relatively%20unknown%20enlightened%20tradition.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20I%20was%20delighted%20to%20see%20this%20post.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20only%20this%20bearded%20Muslim%20on%20the%20mobile%20screen%2C%20but%20many%20of%20his%20predecessors%20had%20indulged%20in%20the%20same%20redemptive%20crime.%20The%20most%20spectacular%20%E2%80%98criminal%E2%80%99%20in%20this%20sphere%20is%20the%20unforgettable%20Kazi%20Nazrul%20Islam%2C%20whom%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20loved%20immeasurably.%20Not%20only%20did%20he%20compose%20heartfelt%20Shymasangeet%20(songs%20devoted%20to%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Shyama%20or%20Kali)%2C%20which%20are%20extremely%20popular%20till%20this%20day%2C%20he%20also%20wrote%20the%20most%20impassioned%20songs%20of%20protest%20and%20was%20the%20first%20to%20translate%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ECommunists%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Internationale%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eanthem%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Einto%20Bengali.%20Nazrul%20was%20a%20phenomenal%20genius.%20Many%20would%20mischievously%20attempt%20to%20bracket%20him%20as%20an%20isolated%20figure%20amongst%20hordes%20of%20seemingly%20%E2%80%98implacable%E2%80%99%20Muslims%2C%20but%20that%20would%20be%20wrong.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20fewer%20than%20five%20more%20Muslim%20Bengali%20poets%20of%20renown%20composed%20prayers%20to%20revere%20Kali.%20Then%2C%20the%20legendary%20Alauddin%20Khan%20of%20Maihar%2C%20also%20the%20father%20of%20the%20sarod%20maestro%20Ali%20Akbar%20Khan%20and%20the%20guru%20of%20Ravi%20Shankar%20was%20an%20ardent%20devotee%20of%20Kali.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F18171537%2FTraditional_Folk_Theatre%25E2%2580%2599s_Artist_performs_Indian_mythological_character-Goddess_Kali-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F18171537%2FTraditional_Folk_Theatre%25E2%2580%2599s_Artist_performs_Indian_mythological_character-Goddess_Kali-1.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F18171537%2FTraditional_Folk_Theatre%25E2%2580%2599s_Artist_performs_Indian_mythological_character-Goddess_Kali-1-300x163.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-608384%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22556%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20folk%20theatre%20practitioner%20portraying%20Hindu%20deity%20Kali.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2F%20Tapas%20Kumar%20Halder%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Muslim%20man%20in%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20phone%20was%20not%20performing%20anything%20unique.%20Indeed%2C%20this%20entire%20tradition%20of%20devotion%20began%20from%20the%20days%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Akbar%20when%20he%20invited%20Brahmin%20pundits%20and%20Hindu%20sages%20to%20%E2%80%98enlighten%E2%80%99%20him%20on%20the%20basic%20tenets%20of%20Hindu%20philosophy%20and%20religion.%20His%20trusted%20lieutenant%2C%20Abul%20Fazl%2C%20who%20wrote%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAin-i-Akbari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20a%20dedicated%20Persian%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Sanskrit%20scholar.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20tradition%20attained%20its%20desirable%20consummation%20when%20emperor%20Shah%20Jahan%E2%80%99s%20first%20son%2C%20Dara%20Shikoh%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Sanskrit%20scholars%2C%20attempted%20to%20translate%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EUpanishads%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20into%20Persian%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Amartya%20Sen%20never%20tires%20of%20recalling%20the%20exemplary%20contribution%20of%20Dara%20Shikoh%2C%20who%20was%20the%20genuine%20forerunner%20of%20the%20Muslim%20man%20on%20the%20screen.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20in%20Bengal%2C%20where%20I%20live%2C%20Valmiki%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20translated%20from%20Sanskrit%20to%20masterly%2C%20readable%20Bengali%20by%20the%20eminent%20poet%20Krittibas%20under%20the%20royal%20patronage%20granted%20by%20the%20Muslim%20ruler%20Nawab%20Alauddin%20Hussain%20Shah%20who%20ruled%20from%201494%20to%201519%20AD.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20modern%20Bengali%20Muslim%20poets%20like%20Jasimuddin%20and%20novelists%20like%20Kayes%20Ahmed%20(this%20frantic%20disciple%20of%20the%20Bengali%20novelist%20Manik%20Bandyopadhyay%20is%20said%20to%20have%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20unable%20to%20accept%20the%20religious%20divide%20of%20Bengal)%2C%20Selina%20Hossain%20and%20Hasan%20Azizul%20Haq%20have%20explored%20parts%20of%20Hindu%20philosophy%20and%20practice%20with%20admirable%20insight.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20work%20of%20Jasimuddin%20is%20replete%20with%20references%20to%20Saraswati%20and%20other%20Hindu%20deities.%20We%20fail%20to%20find%2C%20however%2C%20a%20reciprocal%20utterance%20of%20the%20Islamic%20worldview%20in%20contemporary%20Bengali%20poetry%20written%20by%20%E2%80%98Hindus%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20though%20many%20poets%20like%20Subhas%20Mukhopadhyay%20and%20Sunil%20Gangopadhyay%20would%20object%20to%20the%20classification%20of%20being%20labelled%20%E2%80%98Hindu%E2%80%99.%20The%20only%20remarkable%20exception%20is%20perhaps%20the%20incomparable%20Jibanananda%20Das%20who%20has%20offered%20the%20most%20superb%20example%20of%20%E2%80%98confluence-poetry%E2%80%99%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERupashi%20Bangla%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(beautiful%20Bengal)%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20poetry%20series%20which%20celebrates%20the%20serenity%20and%20beauty%20of%20rural%20Bengal.%20Muslim%20and%20Hindu%20freedom-fighters%20have%20carried%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERupashi%20Bangla%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20their%20knapsacks%20while%20marching%20onto%20the%20battlefield%20to%20fight%20for%20liberation%20for%20Bangladesh.%20It%20was%20both%2C%20their%20inspirational%20mantra%20and%20ajan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06131203%2FScreenshot-2024-01-06-at-1.11.59%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221098%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06131203%2FScreenshot-2024-01-06-at-1.11.59%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201098w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06131203%2FScreenshot-2024-01-06-at-1.11.59%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x160.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06131203%2FScreenshot-2024-01-06-at-1.11.59%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x547.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691829%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Shatranj%20Ke%20Khilari.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20why%20do%20I%20defend%20the%20confluence%20of%20cultures%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20speak%20at%20a%20symposium%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EConfluence%20and%20Continuity%20of%20Culture%20and%20Creativity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20did%20not%20want%20to%20indulge%20in%20abstruse%20and%20postmodern%20theorising%20and%20complex%20debates%20on%20the%20modules%20of%20culture.%20So%2C%20I%20chose%20an%20elementary%20example%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20know%20nothing%20about%20the%20subject.%20But%20my%20wife%20and%20daughter%2C%20who%20are%20simply%20devoted%20to%20Kathak%20as%20artistes%2C%20have%20assured%20me%20again%20and%20again%20that%20Kathak%2C%20unlike%20Bharatnatyam%20and%20Kathakali%2C%20is%20the%20only%20Indian%20classical%20dance%20that%20has%20imbibed%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20influences.%20It%20did%20not%20emerge%20from%20temples%20but%20from%20simple%20quotidian%20life%20(assemblies%20and%20marketplaces)%3B%20it%20narrated%20stories%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKathakata%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20one%20of%20its%20greatest%20patrons%20was%20Nawab%20Wazid%20Azid%20Ali%20Shah%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20who%20himself%20played%20the%20role%20of%20Krishna%20in%20the%20enthralling%20performances%20held%20in%20the%20royal%20household.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20audience%20seemed%20to%20accept%20my%20interpretation.%20But%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etilakdhari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20man%20in%20a%20tilak%20%E2%80%93%20stood%20up.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20nothing.%20You%20are%20a%20paid%20agent%20of%20the%20godless%20communists.%20Kathak%20is%20a%20100%25%20Hindu%2C%20temple%20dance.%20And%20how%20dare%20the%20infernal%20infidel%20Wazid%20Ali%20impersonate%20our%20beloved%20Krishna!%20Our%20days%20are%20coming%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20sanitise%20Kathak%20and%20purge%20it%20of%20all%20its%20supposed%20Muslim%20influence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20He%20was%20guided%20out%20of%20the%20hall%20by%20an%20audience%20who%20seemed%20less%20inclined%20to%20want%20to%20hear%20him%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20here%2C%20in%20the%20land%20of%20Ishwarchandra%20Vidyasagar%20and%20Rabindranath%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%20A%20person%20like%20the%20one%20I%20have%20described%20would%20have%20certainly%20spat%20on%20the%20Muslim%20man%20reciting%20Sanskrit%20shlokas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20we%20are%20celebrating%20the%20imperishable%20cultural%20legacy%20of%20Nawab%20Wazid%20Ali%20Shah%20in%20Kolkata%20at%20present.%20Shah%20was%20banished%20to%20this%20city%20after%20the%20British%20dethroned%20him%20in%20Lucknow.%20Do%20recall%20Premchand%E2%80%99s%20glorious%20story%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESatranj%20Ki%20Khilari%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20equally%20glorious%20film%20bearing%20the%20same%20title%20created%20by%20Satyajit%20Ray.%20He%20was%20exiled%20from%20Lucknow%20186%20years%20ago%20and%20this%20Islamised%20version%20of%20Krishna%2C%20who%20revelled%20dancing%20with%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egopinis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20the%20words%20of%20his%20great-great-grandson%2C%20Shyaheryaer%20Ali%20Mirza%2C%20pronounced%20only%20three%20days%20ago%20%E2%80%9Cchampioned%20humanity%20and%20inter-faith%20harmony.%20We%20want%20to%20revive%20that%20spirit%20and%20culture%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20wholeheartedly%20greeted%20the%20spirit%20and%20practice%20related%20to%20confluence%20of%20cultures.%20We%20have%20rejected%20outright%20Samuel%20Huntington%E2%80%99s%20poisonous%20thesis%20on%20the%20clash%20of%20civilisations.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20revere%20the%20unparalleled%20Johann%20Wolfgang%20von%20Goethe%20who%20consciously%20moved%20out%20of%20his%20predetermined%20Occidental%20parameters%20to%20learn%20Devanagari%20and%20welcome%20Kalidasa%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAbighanam%20Sakuntala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20plays%20ever%20written%20where%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20flower%20and%20fruit%20have%20merged%20into%20an%20indivisible%20whole%E2%80%9D.%20Later%2C%20he%20accepted%20the%20great%20Persian%20poet%20Hafiz%20as%20his%20supreme%20guru%2C%20who%20inspired%20him%20to%20write%20the%20unique%20%3Cem%3EWest-%C3%B6stlicher%20Diwan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bengali%20audience%20member%E2%80%99s%20outrage%20at%20the%20symposium%20has%20not%20alarmed%20me%20because%20the%20present%20dispensation%20will%20encourage%20many%20more%20such%20elements.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20can%20suggest%20one%2C%20outstanding%2C%20corrective%20for%20him%20%E2%80%93%20Khitimohan%20Sen%E2%80%99s%20lucid%20and%20unique%20text%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu-Muslimer%20Jukto%20Sadhana%2FThe%20Joint%20Dedication%20of%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20author%20of%20this%20classic%2C%20which%20records%20the%20remarkable%20and%20harmonious%20contributions%20of%20both%20the%20communities%20to%20the%20spheres%20of%20music%2C%20poetry%2C%20art%20and%20architecture%2C%20from%20the%2016%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20onwards%2C%20was%20a%20formidable%20scholar%20of%20Persian%20and%20Sanskrit.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20closest%20associates%20of%20Tagore%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Vishwabharati%2C%20excavated%20the%20priceless%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDohas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Kabir%20and%20translated%20them%20into%20Bengali.%20He%20is%20the%20also%20the%20grandfather%20of%20the%20hounded%20apostle%20of%20secular%20humanism%2C%20Amartya%20Sen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Above%20all%2C%20he%20wrote%20the%20first%20complete%20text%20on%20Hinduism%20which%20is%20not%20prescribed%20as%20a%20readable%20text%20by%20the%20present%20dispensation%20because%20his%20version%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20as%20well%20as%20that%20of%20another%20illustrious%20interpreter%2C%20Sarvepalli%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20do%20not%20echo%20the%20aggressive%20Hindutva%20of%20Veer%20Savarkar%20and%20Guru%20Golwalkar.%20Heavens%20would%20fall%20on%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20blind%20devotees%20of%20the%20latter%20if%20they%20see%20a%20Muslim%20man%20reciting%20Sanskrit%20texts%2C%20while%20I%20and%20many%20others%20like%20me%20would%20embrace%20him%20with%20open%20arms.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20shall%20be%20equally%20delighted%2C%20if%20not%20ecstatic%2C%20when%20the%20mobile%20screen%20of%20my%20son%20shows%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etilakdhari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Brahmin%20reciting%20the%20fervent%20poems%20of%20St.%20Francis%20of%20Assissi%2C%20or%20better%20still%2C%20quote%20from%20the%20metaphysical%20treatise%20of%20the%20illustrious%20philosopher%20Ibn-i-Rushd%20or%20Averroes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%20Subhoranjan%20Dasgupta%20is%20a%20former%20professor%20of%20human%20sciences%2C%20author%20of%20several%20books%20in%20English%20and%20Bengali%2C%20and%20a%20columnist.%20He%20is%20based%20in%20Kolkata.%20His%20email%20is%20srdasgup19%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704527031000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06130952%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwajid-ali-shah-confluence-hindu-muslim%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indians%20have%20often%20wholeheartedly%20greeted%20the%20spirit%20and%20practice%20related%20to%20the%20confluence%20of%20cultures.%20And%20yet%2C%20a%20recent%20experience%20tells%20me%20we%20have%20managed%20to%20stray%20far%20enough.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwajid-ali-shah-confluence-hindu-muslim%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Rohit%20are%20still%20great%20fielders%3A%20Gavaskar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2