r%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-navy-trying-to-hunt-down-pirates-involved-in-hijacking-attempt-124010600276_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Findian-navy-trying-to-hunt-down-pirates-involved-in-hijacking-attempt-124010600276_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Findian-navy-trying-to-hunt-down-pirates-involved-in-hijacking-attempt-124010600276_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Priest%20Removed%20From%20Church%20Post%20After%20Joining%20BJP%2C%20Had%20Led%2047%20Families%20to%20Formally%20Join%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06130147%2FGCmGRU2agAAf2iH.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20latest%20outreach%20to%20the%20sizeable%20Christian%20community%20in%20Kerala%20has%20led%20to%C2%A0%20controversy%20with%20a%20priest%2C%20who%20had%20led%20a%20clutch%20of%2047%20families%20to%20formally%20join%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20this%20past%20week%2C%20being%20divested%20of%20all%20Church-related%20responsibilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20exactly%20why%20the%20priest%20has%20been%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20this%20action%20as%20the%20church%20has%20told%20some%20papers%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20not%20exactly%20spurred%20by%20his%20joining%20of%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20press%20note%20released%20by%20the%20Malankara%20Orthodox%20Syrian%20Church%20on%20January%205%2C%20the%20priest%2C%20Ferdinand%20Shaiju%20Kurian%20who%20served%20as%20secretary%20of%20the%20Church%E2%80%99s%20Nilackal%20diocese%2C%20was%20removed%20from%20all%20official%20responsibilities%20after%20the%20church%20received%20%E2%80%9Csome%20complaints%20from%20the%20diocese%20members.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20press%20note%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20meeting%20of%20the%20diocese%20council%20was%20held%20on%20January%204%20which%20decided%20to%20form%20an%20inquiry%20commission%20to%20probe%20the%20allegations%20against%20Fr.%20Kurian%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20within%20two%20months.%20During%20the%20period%20of%20investigation%2C%20Fr.%20Shaiju%20has%20been%20taken%20off%20of%20his%20official%20responsibilities%20within%20the%20Church.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFr.%20Shaiju%20had%20joined%20the%20BJP%20along%20with%2047%20Christian%20families%20this%20past%20December%2030%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20V%20Muraleedharan%20at%20Pathanamitha.%20The%20news%20had%20hit%20the%20headlines%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20seen%20wooing%20Christian%20voters%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20in%20Kerala.%20This%20effort%20also%20included%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20interacting%20with%20a%20set%20of%20Kerala-based%20church%20leaders.%20Local%20party%20members%20had%20gone%20door%20to%20door%20in%20December%20to%20greet%20Christian%20families%20on%20Christmas.%20As%20much%20as%2019%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20the%20state%20is%20Christian.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnot-in-our-name-over-3000-christians-dissociate-from-pm-modis-christmas-lunch%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Not%20in%20Our%20Name%E2%80%99%3A%20Over%203%2C000%20Christians%20Dissociate%20From%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Christmas%20Lunch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202019%20parliamentary%20polls%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20unit%20president%20K.%20Surendran%20had%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20from%20the%20Pathanamthitta%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20which%20has%20a%20sizeable%20Christian%20population.%20Fr.%20Kurian%E2%80%99s%20Nilackal%20diocese%20comes%20under%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%20The%20priest%2C%20while%20taking%20up%20the%20BJP%20membership%2C%20had%20stated%20that%20his%20decision%20was%20based%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20development%20initiatives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20soon%20after%20his%20joining%20the%20right%20wing%20party%20along%20with%2047%20Christian%20families%2C%20a%20section%20of%20people%20from%20within%20the%20community%20took%20out%20a%20march%20to%20the%20diocese%20headquarters%20at%20Ranni%20in%20protest.%20What%20followed%20was%20a%20litany%20of%20complaints%20against%20the%20priest%20from%20diocesan%20members%2C%20including%20misconduct%20towards%20a%20woman%20%E2%80%93%20leading%20the%20Church%20to%20institute%20a%20probe.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20fellow%20priest%2C%20Father%20Mathews%20Vazhakunnam%2C%20made%20allegations%20against%20F.%20Kurian%20in%20a%20local%20TV%20channel%20too%2C%20leading%20the%20church%20to%20state%20in%20the%20press%20note%20that%20the%20committee%20would%20look%20into%20why%20he%20had%20raised%20those%20complaints%20against%20a%20fellow%20priest%20in%20a%20TV%20debate%20than%20doing%20it%20within%20the%20platform%20of%20the%20church.%20An%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbjp-christian-church-priest-kerala-9096940%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoting%20church%20sources%20said%20that%20Vazhakunnam%20%E2%80%9Chad%20a%20pro-CPI(M)%20stance.%20During%20the%20previous%20LDF%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20had%20served%20as%20a%20director%20of%20the%20state-run%20Minority%20Development%20Finance%20Corporation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFather%20Saiju%20was%20removed%20from%20his%20roles%20not%20for%20having%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20At%20present%2C%20the%20Orthodox%20Church%20has%20not%20taken%20any%20stand%20on%