ited%20for%20the%20bus%20to%20come%20back%20and%20realised%20that%20someone%20took%20them.%20There%20was%20no%20signal%20inside%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20area%20to%20track%20the%20device.%20And%20when%20I%20finally%20did%2C%20it%20was%20already%20on%20the%20move%2C%20and%20was%20in%20another%20national%20park%20about%2040km%20from%20where%20I%20was.%20But%20the%20next%20day%20I%20could%20track%20it%20to%20a%20hotel%20nearby%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jain%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jain%20said%20he%20then%20approached%20the%20hotel%20along%20with%20the%20Kerala%20police%2C%20but%20they%20could%20not%20do%20much%20as%20the%20location%20did%20not%20pinpoint%20to%20any%20exact%20room%20and%20the%20hotel%20authorities%20refused%20to%20help%20further%20citing%20client%20privilege.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20watched%20my%20device%20travel%20through%20Mangalore%20to%20Goa.%20When%20it%20stayed%20put%20in%20Goa%2C%20I%20figured%20the%20person%20is%20from%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jain%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Stonks%20Studio%2C%20a%20social%20media%20content%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2021%2C%202023%20Mr%20Jain%20(%40niquotein)%20posted%20on%20X%20along%20with%20location%20coordinates%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20recently%20lost%20my%20new%20airpods%20in%20kerala%20and%20this%20**%20person%20is%20travelling%20with%20it.%20the%20person%20is%20in%20south%20goa%20since%202%20days%2C%20so%20I'm%20guessing%20they%20live%20there.%20does%20anyone%20here%20live%20around%20dr.%20alvaro%20de%20loyola%20furtado%20road%20in%20south%20goa%3F%20rt%20for%20reach%2C%20etc%20(sic).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E**%20The%20sleuths%20from%20X%20took%20over.%20Within%20minutes%2C%20user%20%40ItsMeAshwin12%20posted%20the%20picture%20of%20the%20house%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Google%20Street%20Map%20along%20with%20the%20message%2C%20%26quot%3BAirpods%20are%20in%20this%20house%2C%20Twitter%2C%20do%20ur%20thing%20and%20go%20get%20them%20(sic).%26quot%3B%20While%20most%20jumped%20into%20the%20conversation%20to%20discuss%20technical%20details%20of%20tracking%20Airpods%2C%20a%20day%20later%2C%20the%20X%20post%20reached%20a%20target%20close%20enough%20%E2%80%93%20the%20neighbour's%20relative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEdward%20Mascarenhas%20(%40Kooledd)%20posted%20on%20December%2022%2C%202023%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20relatives%20stay%20exactly%20there%20and%20I%20sent%20them%20the%20deets.%20They%20mentioned%20their%20neighbors%20did%20go%20to%20Kerala%20recently%20(sic).%26quot%3B%20He%20then%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20another%20post%3A%20%26quot%3BSo%20they%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20them%20and%20they%20mentioned%20they'll%20drop%20it%20off%20at%20Margoa%20police%20station%20(sic).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20December%2022%20evening%2C%20the%20device%20was%20at%20Margoa%20police%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jain%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jain%20said%20he%20then%20called%20the%20police%20station.%20%26quot%3BThey%20confirmed%20that%20the%20device%20was%20indeed%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20remaining%20for%20him%20was%20to%20collect%20it.%20%26quot%3BMany%20from%20X%2C%20of%20course%2C%20volunteered.%20But%20my%20friend%20and%20former%20colleague%2C%20Sanket%20(%40iamsexified)%20chipped%20in%2C%20saying%20he%20will%20be%20going%20to%20Goa%20in%20a%20few%20days%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20wait%20for%20him%20to%20collect%20the%20device%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20last%20night%2C%20Mr%20Jain%20posted%20in%20X%2C%20with%20a%20picture%20of%20Sanket%20triumphantly%20holding%20the%20device%3A%20%26quot%3BCAN%20U%20BELIEVE!!%3F%20thank%20u%20to%20angel%20sanket%2C%20goa%20police%2C%20kerala%20police%2C%20twitter%2C%20find%20my%20feature%2C%20twitter%20and%20everyone%20who%20replied%20to%20this%20tweet!%20what%20a%20beautiful%20story.%20what%20a%20community-like%20feeling.%20world%20is%20so%20big%20and%20yet%20small%20(sic).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20post%2C%20which%20saw%201.2%20million%20views%2C%20became%20a%20target%20for%20some%20new-age%20guerrilla%20marketing%20too.%20Within%20a%20few%20hours%20of%20the%20post%2C%20Ather%20Energy%20(%40atherenergy)%20jumped%20in%20with%20an%20offer%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20fully%20charged%2C%20mission-ready%20Ather%20450X%20waiting%20for%20you%20at%20Margoa.%20Over%20and%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bengaluru-based%20bakery%20went%20a%20step%20further%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20buzz.%20It%20quickly%20opened%20X%20account%2C%20%40bitesofben48552%2C%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20and%20posted%20its%20offer%3A%20%26quot%3BWe've%20just%20joined%20%40X%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20we're%20dispatching%20a%20package%20of%20quick%20bites%20to%20ensure%20you're%20fueled%20for%20your%20crucial%20mission.%20Hopefully%2C%20we're%20not%20late.%20Kindly%20share%20your%20address%2C%20and%20we'll%20deliver%20it%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20your%20doorstep.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jain%20said%20although%20he%20or%20Sanket%20did%20not%20use%20any%20of%20these%20offers%2C%20the%20thought%20counted.%20%26quot%3BIt%20made%20me%20feel%20good%20about%20the%20entire%20incident.%20Although%20initially%20I%20was%20pissed%20off%20with%20the%20person%20who%20walked%20away%20with%20my%20Airpod%2C%20I%20am%20grateful%20that%20they%20went%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20handed%20over%20the%20device.%20They%20could%20have%20easily%20chucked%20it%20somewhere%20and%20that%20would%20have%20made%20it%20a%20lot%20more%20complicated%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20to%20prove%20his%20point%2C%20another%20X%20user%2C%20Ritesh%20Ambastha%20(%40riteshambastha)%20posted%3A%20%26quot%3BI've%20lost%20the%20Airpod%20in%20the%20house%20I'm%20living%20in%3B%20and%20it's%20been%203%20months%20I'm%20looking%20for%20it.%20I%20wish%20you%20the%20best%