ne%20Barnett%20has%20responded%20to%20claims%20made%20by%20Natalia%20Grace%20in%20the%20new%20docuseries%20about%20her%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20Curious%20Case%20of%20Natalia%20Grace%2C%26quot%3B%20Natalia%20accuses%20Barnett%20of%20physically%20abusing%20her.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBarnett%20called%20Natalia%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bsociopath%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20desperate%20for%20attention%20in%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKristine%20Barnett%20called%20her%20former%20adopted%20daughter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnatalia-grace-real-age-where-is-she-now-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENatalia%20Grace%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%26quot%3Bsociopath%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKristineElizabethPearson%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02seNwGr8aLqhUewHddtuNqNTDiv5gkgaKdG7Sz3B5B5uXzMgGSAzUtk8ZnxWKb38Rl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewide-ranging%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20publicly%20posted%20to%20Facebook%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarnett's%20statement%20comes%20after%20Investigation%20Discovery%20followed%20up%20its%20May%202023%20docuseries%20%26quot%3BThe%20Curious%20Case%20of%20Natalia%20Grace%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20second%20part%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BNatalia%20Speaks%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20aired%20in%20early%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20episodes%2C%20Natalia%20Grace%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20and%20later%20adopted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnatalia-grace-parents-where-are-michael-kristine-barnett-now-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKristine%20and%20Michael%20Barnett%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202010%2C%20accuses%20her%20former%20adoptive%20mother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnatalia-grace-dna-test-age-parents-abuse-allegations-shocking-accusations-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20physical%20abuse%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Natalia%20also%20says%20that%20the%20Barnetts%20legally%20changed%20her%20age%20to%2022%20and%20forced%20her%20to%20live%20on%20her%20own%20in%20Indiana%2C%20when%20she%20was%20in%20reality%20only%20about%20nine%20years%20old.%20(The%20Barnetts%20were%20later%20charged%20by%20an%20Indiana%20court%20with%20neglect%20of%20a%20dependent.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKristine%20Barnett%20vehemently%20denied%20the%20accusations%20in%20her%20Facebook%20statement%2C%20writing%20that%20Natalia%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20abused%20by%20anyone%20in%20my%20family%E2%80%A6%20Nobody%20ever%20took%20a%20belt%20to%20Natalia%20and%20the%20allegations%20that%20she%20was%20'beaten'%20are%20just%20plain%20false.%20Any%20discipline%20of%20Natalia%20was%20very%20minimal%20and%20was%20not%20out%20of%20the%20bounds%20of%20normal%20parenting.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20called%20the%20docuseries%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20sensationalized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarnett%20went%20on%20to%20refute%20Natalia's%20claims%20that%20she%20was%20effectively%20abandoned%20by%20her%20adoptive%20parents%20when%20she%20moved%20into%20an%20apartment%20on%20her%20own%2C%20citing%20court%20rulings%2C%20and%20said%20she%20tried%20to%20help%20Natalia%20as%20best%20she%20could%20before%20Natalia%20chose%20to%20live%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnatalia-speaks-ending-explained-natalia-grace-new-parents-antwon-cynthia-mans-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Mans%20family%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Barnett%2C%20through%20numerous%20hospital%20visits%20and%20trips%20to%20therapy%20with%20Natalia%2C%20she%20eventually%20came%20to%20a%20realization%20about%20Natalia's%20mental%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20end%20I%20learned%20she%20is%20a%20sociopath%2C%26quot%3B%20Barnett%20wrote%20of%20her%20former%20daughter.%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20have%20not%20wrapped%20my%20head%20around%20that%20diagnosis%20to%20this%20day%20honestly%20and%20I%20still%20revert%20to%20feeling%20sympathy