0Pointless%20a%20test%20being%20over%20so%20fast%20you%20don't%20even%20see%20a%20hint%20of%20a%20crack.%3Cbr%3E%5CnPitches%20deteriorate%20over%20the%20days%2C%20let%20it%20happen.%20Two%20day%20tests%20are...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dale%20Steyn%20(%40DaleSteyn62)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDaleSteyn62%2Fstatus%2F1742871866337812717%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20after%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20interesting%20analysis%20on%20the%20pitch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20saw%20what%20happened%20in%20this%20Test%20match%20and%20how%20the%20pitch%20played.%20I%20honestly%20don't%20mind%20playing%20on%20pitches%20like%20these.%20As%20long%20as%20everyone%20keeps%20their%20mouth%20shut%20and%20don't%20talk%20too%20much%20about%20Indian%20pitches%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20you%20come%20here%20to%20challenge%20yourself.%20Yes%2C%20it%20is%20dangerous.%20It%20is%20challenging.%20So%2C%20and%20when%20people%20come%20to%20India%2C%20it%20is%20again%20pretty%20challenging%20as%20well.%20Look%2C%20when%20you%20are%20here%20to%20play%20Test%20cricket%2C%20we%20talk%20about%20Test%20cricket%2C%20the%20ultimate%20prize%2C%20Test%20cricket%20being%20the%20pinnacle%20and%20stuff%20like%20that.%20I%20think%20it's%20important%20that%20we%20also%20stand%20by%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20(6%2F61%20in%2013.5%20overs)%2C%20the%20master%20practitioner%20of%20fast%20bowling%2C%20knocked%20the%20stuffing%20out%20of%20South%20Africa's%20middle-order%20in%20a%20menacing%20morning%20spell%20though%20Aiden%20Markram%20(106%20off%20103%20balls)%20fought%20like%20a%20lone%20ranger%20on%20a%20burning%20deck%20to%20take%20South%20Africa%20to%20176%20in%2036.5%20overs%20at%20stroke%20of%20lunch%20on%20day%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20paltry%20target%20even%20on%20the%20toughest%20of%20tracks%20wasn't%20exactly%20a%20ta