d-92-13042939%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brazilian%20football%20legend%20Mario%20Zagallo%20has%20died%20aged%2092.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmario-zagallo-brazilian-football-legend-dies-aged-92-13042939%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmario-zagallo-brazilian-football-legend-dies-aged-92-13042939%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmario-zagallo-brazilian-football-legend-dies-aged-92-13042939%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Lawyer%20Who%20Bought%20Dawood's%20Plot%20For%20Rs%202%20Crore%20Wants%20To%20Build%20There%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20lawyer%20who%20bought%20a%20plot%20owned%20by%20underworld%20don%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20in%20Maharashtra%20for%20a%20whopping%20Rs%202%20crore%20yesterday%2C%20says%20he%20intends%20to%20build%20a%20Sanatan%20school%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20Srivastava%2C%20a%20former%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%2C%20said%20he%20paid%20such%20a%20huge%20amount%20for%20the%20plot%20because%20the%20survey%20number%20and%20the%20amount%20add%20up%20to%20a%20figure%20in%20numerology%20that%20works%20in%20his%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20Sanatani%20Hindu%20and%20we%20follow%20our%20panditji.%20The%20survey%20number%20(of%20the%20plot)%20and%20the%20amount%20have%20a%20figure%20that%20goes%20in%20my%20favour%20according%20to%20numerology.%20I%20will%20start%20a%20Sanatan%20school%20on%20this%20plot%20after%20getting%20it%20converted%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Srivastava%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Srivastava%20had%20earlier%20purchased%20three%20of%20the%20underworld%20don's%20properties%2C%20including%20his%20childhood%20home%20in%20the%20same%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20auction%20in%20March%202001%2C%20in%20which%20Mr%20Srivastava%20was%20the%20only%20bidder%2C%20the%20lawyer%20had%20bought%20two%20shops%20