0in%202014%20and%202018.%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20administration%20levied%20human%20rights%20sanctions%20against%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20elite%20paramilitary%20force%20Rapid%20Action%20Battalion%20and%20several%20of%20its%20former%20officials%20following%20accusations%20of%20severe%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%20including%20hundreds%20of%20enforced%20disappearances%20and%20extrajudicial%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20relationships%20do%20not%20exist%20in%20a%20zero-sum%20vacuum%2C%20where%20every%20nation%20is%20looking%20to%20exert%20their%20own%20individual%20will%20on%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20US%20are%20perceived%20to%20be%20allies%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20hard%20work%20done%20on%20growing%20the%20relationship%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Washington%20has%20seen%20a%20closer%20diplomatic%20relationship%20culminate%20in%20the%20Quad%2C%20along%20with%20Australia%20and%20Japan%2C%20aimed%20almost%20entirely%20at%20deterring%20China%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20US%20sits%20apart%20from%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20argues%20it%20is%20in%20its%20national%20interest%20that%20Hasina%E2%80%99s%20government%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%20however%20could%20be%20perceived%20as%20somewhat%20thin%20under%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20keynote%20speech%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20foreign%20minister%2C%20M.J.%20Akbar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fnews%2Fbangladesh%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnews%2Fsuperpowers-want-puppets-pretend-serve-bangladesh-3496971%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20superpowers%20want%20puppets%20who%20can%20serve%20their%20interest%20because%20Bangladesh%20is%20important%20geopolitically.%20Akbar%20termed%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cliberator%20of%20democracy%20from%20dictatorship%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20all%20the%20globally%20accepted%20indicators%20for%20freedom%20and%20democracy%20contradict%20Akbar%E2%80%99s%20claim.%20The%20statement%20shows%20the%20general%20sentiment%20of%20the%20Indian%20establishment%20towards%20Bangladesh%3A%20that%20Hasina%E2%80%99s%20rule%20satisfies%20Indian%20aims%20regardless%20of%20the%20trouble%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20wins%20and%20who%20loses%20may%20be%20obvious%20to%20the%20pundits%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20but%20the%20weight%20that%20it%20will%20put%20on%20the%20US%20and%20India%20relationship%20will%20continue%20long%20after%20the%20vote%2C%20with%20an%20%E2%80%9Cagree%20to%20disagree%20mentality%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0likely%20to%20test%20the%20burgeoning%20friendship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hf.uio.no%2Fikos%2Fenglish%2Fpeople%2Faca%2Fstudy-of-religion%2Ftemporary%2Fmubashh%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EDr%20Mubashar%20Hasan%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20is%20a%20postdoctoral%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Culture%20Studies%20and%20Oriental%20Languages%2C%20University%20of%20Oslo%2C%20Norway.%20His%20research%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20Norwegian%20Research%20Council.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20under%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ECreative%20Commons%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F360info.org%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E360info%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%84%A2.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704511854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FSheikh_Hasina1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladeshs-crumbling-democracy-no-roadblock-for-superpowers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20longest-serving%20female%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20will%20extend%20her%20reign%20because%20her%20main%20oppositio