with%20girls%20who%20looked%2011%20years%20old%20in%202018%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20registered%20sex%20offender%20has%20also%20refused%20investigators%20from%20entering%20his%20island%20and%20instead%20met%20them%20at%20his%20office.%20The%20lawsuit%20also%20claims%20that%20a%2015-year-old%20girl%2C%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20forced%20to%20perform%20sex%20acts%20on%20others%20by%20Epstein%2C%20once%20tried%20to%20run%20away%20from%20the%20island%20but%20was%20caught%20and%20held%20captive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20email%20Epstein%20sent%20to%20Maxwell%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20the%20recent%20unsealed%20documents%2C%20it%20was%20claimed%20that%20late%20scientist%20Stephen%20Hawking%20had%20taken%20part%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bunderage%20orgy%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20island.%20People%20magazine%20reported%20that%20Mr%20Hawking%20visited%20Epstein's%20private%20island%20as%20part%20of%20a%20science%20trip%20in%202006%2C%20months%20before%20he%20was%20first%20charged%20with%20sexual%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704511560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fldm4uhgg_imran-ghislaine_625x300_06_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Flies-you-muppet-pakistan-cricket-great-fumes-over-post-linking-him-and-imran-khan-to-epstein-island-4809428%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2072-acre%20property%2C%20also%20known%20informally%20as%20%26quot%3BPaedophile%20Island%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20places%20where%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20reportedly%20held%20sex%20parties%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Flies-you-muppet-pakistan-cricket-great-fumes-over-post-linking-him-and-imran-khan-to-epstein-island-4809428%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Flies-you-muppet-pakistan-