%20Jahan%20Sheikh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BED%20team%20with%20CRPF%20personnel%20was%20attacked%20by%20800-1%2C000%20people%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20cause%20death%20as%20these%20people%20were%20carrying%20weapons%20such%20as%20lathis%2C%20stones%20and%20bricks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ED%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrested%20Trinamool%20leader%20Sankar%20Adhaya%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20ED's%20regional%20headquarters%20in%20Kolkata's%20Salt%20Lake.%20His%20medical%20test%20will%20be%20done%20today%20and%20he%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20a%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Governor%20last%20night%20summoned%20top%20Bengal%20officials%20to%20meet%20him%20over%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20ED%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20ghastly%20incident.%20It%20is%20alarming%20and%20deplorable.%20It%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20a%20civilised%20government%20to%20stop%20barbarism%20and%20vandalism%20in%20a%20democracy.%20If%20a%20government%20fails%20in%20its%20basic%20duty%2C%20then%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20will%20take%20its%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20Governor%20CV%20Anand%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20ED%20officers%20marked%20a%20big%20escalation%20in%20the%20friction%20between%20the%20government%20led%20by%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20the%20ED%2C%20a%20central%20agency%20that%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20time%20and%20again%20accused%20of%20working%20in%20a%20biased%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Bengal%20BJP%20chief%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20sought%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20anti-terror%20group%20National%20Investigation%20Team%20(NIA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20Suvendu%20Adhukari%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Bengal%2C%20took%20direct%20aim%20at%20Ms%20Banerjee%20over%20law%20and%20order%20issues%20in%20her%20state.%20%26quot%3B...%20Due%20to%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20assurance%20and%20encouragement%2C%20criminals%20like%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20have%20assembled%20Rohingya%20to%20work%20as%20his%20henchmen%20and%20establish%20a%20reign%20of%20terror%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adhikari%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20officers%20had%20to%20leave%20their%20vehicles%20and%20take%20autorickshaws%20and%20two-wheelers%20to%20reach%20a%20safe%20place%20out%20of%20Sandeskhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704511440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fp5b7og88_ed-bengal-attack_625x300_05_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-arrests-trinamool-leader-shankar-adhya-day-after-attack-on-officers-4809456%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20made%20another%20arrest%20in%20the%20alleged%20ration%20scam%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20agency%20had%20arrested%20Trinamool%20Congress%20minister%20Jyotipriya%20Mullick%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-arrests-trinamool-leader-shankar-adhya-day-after-attack-on-officers-4809456%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-arrests-trinamool-leader-shankar-adhya-day-after-attack-on-officers-4809456%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-arrests-trinamool-leader-shankar-adhya-day-after-attack-on-officers-4809456%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hrithik-Saba%20make%20stylish%20appearance%20at%20airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704511369000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106588159%2Cimgsize-39952.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fe