h%20professor%20John%20Guillebaud%2C%20who%20told%20Quartz%20that%20patients%20have%20described%20cramp%20pain%20as%20%26quot%3Balmost%20as%20bad%20as%20having%20a%20heart%20attack.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20gynecologist%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrjengunter.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jen%20Gunter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20writes%20a%20popular%20women's%20health%20blog%2C%20took%20that%20comparison%20one%20step%20further%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrjengunter.com%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2Fcomparing-period-cramps-with-heart-attacks-isnt-useful-or-accurate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20period%20cramps%20are%20often%20much%20%3Cem%3Emore%20%3C%2Fem%3Epainful%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmassive-heart-attack-signs-women-flu-symptoms-2023-12%5C%22%3Eheart%20attacks%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20can%20often%20be%20quite%20mild.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20waiting%20for%20terrible%2C%20excruciating%20chest%20pain%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20you%20are%20having%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20well%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20miss%20the%20heart%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20Gunter%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BHeart%20attacks%20often%20produce%20vague%20symptoms%20or%20mild%20pain%2C%20that%20is%20why%20many%20people%20ignore%20them%20...%20In%20addition%2C%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20women%20have%20no%20pain%20with%20heart%20attacks.%20It%20would%20be%20dangerous%20for%20women%20to%20think%20that%20a%20heart%20attack%20should%20be%20at%20least%20as%20bad%20as%20their%20menstrual%20cramps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20are%20period%20cramps%20so%20painful%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22menstrual%20cramps%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F590a3c8d2c835b1e008b468f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5