udent%2C%20who%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20hinted%2C%20is%20his%20lover.%20In%20the%20scene%2C%20as%20we%20see%20Bernstein%20not%20just%20taking%20drugs%20but%20also%20holding%20up%20the%20tray%20and%20serving%20his%20manager%20and%20the%20young%20man%2C%20what%20stands%20out%20is%20how%20bereft%20of%20judgement%20it%20all%20feels.%20The%20way%20the%20camera%20(by%20cinematographer%20Matthew%20Libatique)%20frames%20the%20three%20characters%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20clammy%2C%20crowded%20rave%2C%20the%20filmmaking%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20casting%20aspersions%20on%20Bernstein.%20The%20scene%20is%20not%20preceded%20by%20overemphasising%20Bernstein%E2%80%99s%20inner%20turmoil%20(he%20had%20been%20living%20away%20from%20his%20wife%20and%20kids%20by%20then)%2C%20correlating%20his%20drug%20habit%20to%20it%2C%20and%20thereby%20%E2%80%98explaining%E2%80%99%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20sequence%20that%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20how%20clear-eyed%20Cooper%20is%20in%20%3Cem%3EMaestro%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20seeing%20the%20man%20trapped%20under%20the%20musical%20phenomenon%2C%20but%20also%20not%20trying%20to%20merely%20contain%20his%20life%20and%20legacy%20into%20a%20few%20words%2C%20scenes%2C%20and%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECooper%20(who%20co-wrote%20the%20film%20with%20Josh%20Singer)%20realises%20the%20futility%20of%20simplifying%20and%20condensing%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20into%20a%20feature-length%20film%2C%20so%20he%20keeps%20alluding%20to%20events%20that%20took%20place%20in%20their%20life%20between%20the%20%E2%80%98scenes%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20film.%20As%20Leonard%20finds%20prominence%20and%20worldwide%20acceptance%20in%20his%20late%2030s%2C%20we%20see%20Felicia%20standing%20in%20the%20wings%20under%20his%20gargantuan%20shadow.%20When%20Leonard%20announces%20he%E2%80%99s%20completed%20writing%20a%20piece%20of%20score%20while%20being%20at%20home%20on%20holiday%20after%20a%20long%20world%20tour%2C%20Felicia%20quietly%20gets%20up%20from%20the%20living%20room%2C%20slips%20out%20of%20the%20window%20and%20jumps%20into%20the%20pool.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20whimsical%2C%20child-like%20action%2C%20but%20one%20that%20also%20conveys%20the%20suffocation%20she%E2%80%99s%20been%20feeling%20while%20being%20married%20to%20him%2C%20which%20has%20slowly%20built%20up%20over%20time.%20The%20scene%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20there%3B%20the%20camera%20comes%20back%20to%20Leonard%E2%80%99s%20face%20who%20lets%20out%20a%20tiny%20laugh%20at%20Felicia%E2%80%99s%20incredulous%20reaction%2C%20only%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20all%20his%20actions%20that%20have%20driven%20her%20to%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgJP2QblqLA0%3Fsi%3DhvIaMfUXdOnmX_eP%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBradley%20Cooper%2C%20who%20announced%20himself%20as%20a%20first-rate%20director%20in%20his%20debut%2C%20%3Cem%3EA%20Star%20Is%20Born%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2018)%2C%20showcases%20his%20singular%20and%20precise%20directorial%20voice%20in%20%3Cem%3EMaestro%3C%2Fem%3E%20too.%20The%20early%20portions%20of%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%E2%80%99s%20resemble%20a%20fairytale%20musical%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9850s%20%E2%80%93%20such%20is%20the%20sweeping%20scale%2C%20when%20things%20seem%20to%20be%20happening%20at%20a%20frightening%20pace.%20In%20an%20early%20scene%2C%20we%20see%20Leonard%20getting%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20phone%20call%20to%20conduct%20with%20the%20New%20York%20Philharmonic%20Orchestra%20at%20the%20Carnegie%20Hall%20(after%20the%20original%20conductor%20falls%20ill)%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20one%20unbroken%20shot%2C%20he%20goes%20from%20his%20loft%20to%20the%20much-revered%20performance%20arena.%20Similarly%2C%20during%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%E2%80%99s%20courtship%2C%20the%20film%20goes%20from%20their%20acquaintance-ship%20to%20him%20showcasing%20his%20musical%20theatre%20work%20to%20her%20in%20an%20inspired%20sequence.%20The%20sequence%20ends%20with%20white%20bed%20sheets%20flying%20over%20them%20on%20stage%2C%20to%20the%20bed%20sheet%20over%20their%20feet%20in%20one%20clean%20cut%20%E2%80%93%20telling%20us%20everything%20about%20their%20growing%20fondness%20and%20intimacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20once%20the%20marriage%20gets%20going%2C%20Libatique%E2%80%99s%20camera%20becomes%20less%20vivacious.%20It%20seems%20to%20be%20observing%20both%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%2C%20staying%20on%20them%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20longer%20after%20a%20%E2%80%98scene%E2%80%99%20has%20ended%20%E2%80%93%20documenting%20the%20unspoken%20feelings%20when%20they%20stopped%20paying%20attention%20to%20each%20other.%20Like%20most%20marriage%20stories%2C%20even%20this%20one%20has%20a%20stellar%20confrontation%20between%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%2C%20when%20he%20comes%20home%20for%20a%20Thanksgiving%20dinner.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20raw%2C%20ruthless%20duel%20of%20words%2C%20impeccably%20performed%20by%20both%20Cooper%20and%20Mulligan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recurring%20complaint%20with%20Cooper%E2%80%99s%20film%20has%20been%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20focus%20on%20Bernstein%E2%80%99s%20musical%20exploits.%20To%20be%20the%20devil%E2%80%99s%20advocate%20here%2C%20instead%20of%20making%20a%20birth-to-death%20biopic%2C%20I%20can%20see%20why%20Cooper%20was%20dazzled%20by%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%E2%80%99s%20love%20story%2C%20offering%20a%20more%20in-depth%20peek%20into%20the%20man%2C%20and%20helps%20us%20understand%20him%20better%2C%20than%20any%20montage%20of%20seeing%20him%20perform.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20bold%20choice%20%E2%80%93%20making%20a%20film%20on%20the%20life%20of%20a%20virtuoso%20%E2%80%93%20where%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20buried%20into%20the%20background%2C%20as%20his%20domestic%20quarrels%20rise%20to%20the%20fore.%20However%2C%20Cooper%20seems%20to%20know%20exactly%20the%20film%20he%E2%80%99s%20making%20and%20dives%20head-long%20into%20it%20with%20the%20same%20passion%20with%20which%20Bernstein%20would%20let%20the%20music%20flow%20through%20him%20while%20conducting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20an%20exceptionally%20acted%20film%2C%20including%20the%20ancillary%20characters%20essayed%20by%20Matt%20Bomer%20and%20Maya%20Hawke%2C%20who%20plays%20his%20daughter%20Jamie.%20Most%20of%20these%20actors%20get%20that%20one%20scene%2C%20where%20they%20communicate%20their%20feelings%20without%20words.%20When%20Leonard%20introduces%20Felicia%20to%20David%20(Bomer)%20%E2%80%93%20his%20ex-lover%2C%20David%20looks%20at%20them%20with%20sorrow%20in%20his%20eyes%20and%20a%20smile%20on%20his%20face.%20Similarly%2C%20when%20Jamie%20is%20told%20to%20ignore%20the%20rumours%20about%20Leonard%20being%20involved%20with%20his%20younger%20students%2C%20you%20see%20her%20nodding%2C%20while%20also%20realising%20what%20kind%20of%20man%20her%20father%20really%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20too%20easy%20to%20say%20that%20Cooper%20means%20this%20film%20to%20be%20an%20acting%20showcase%20for%20himself%2C%20channelling%20Bernstein%E2%80%99s%20throaty%20voice%2C%20his%20relaxed%20body%20language%2C%20and%20a%20mind%20that%20could%20never%20stop%20racing%2C%20going%20through%20projects%2C%20performances%2C%20spouses%2C%20lovers%2C%20experiences%2C%20always%20anxious%20to%20get%20to%20the%20next%20thing.%20If%20anything%2C%20Cooper%E2%80%99s%20performance%20as%20Leonard%20Bernstein%20is%20the%20opposite%20of%20a%20vanity%20project.%20And%20we%20know%20this%20for%20how%20Cooper%20entrusts%20the%20stage%20to%20Mulligan%20in%20the%20second%20hour%2C%20making%20Felicia%20the%20protagonist%20of%20the%20film%2C%20as%20Leonard%20remains%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20Mulligan%E2%80%99s%20deeply-affecting%20performance%20as%20Felicia%20that%20lies%20at%20the%20core%20of%20%3Cem%3EMaestro%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Mulligan%2C%20known%20for%20her%20stoic%20face%20while%20depicting%20total%20and%20complete%20devastation%20in%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3EAn%20Education%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2009)%2C%20%3Cem%3EWildlife%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2018)%2C%C2%A0%20employs%20it%20to%20great%20effect%20here%2C%20wordlessly%20conveying%20the%20humiliation%20of%20being%20wedded%20to%20a%20genius.%20Like%20in%20his%20directorial%20debut%2C%20Cooper%20seems%20smitten%20by%20the%20idea%20of%20unpacking%20the%20loneliness%20of%20icons%20and%20examining%20them%20for%20all%20their%20contradictions%2C%20transgressions%2C%20and%20what%20lights%20up%20their%20mind%20every%20morning.%20It%E2%80%99s%20fitting%20then%20that%20Cooper%E2%80%99s%20film%20becomes%20a%20tribute%20to%20Felicia%20%E2%80%93%20a%20choice%20Bernstein%20would%20have%20approved%20of%2C%20even%20if%20the%20film%20is%20named%20after%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704464346000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05192303%2FEffect-58.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmaestro-bradley-coopers-biopic-of-leonard-bernstein-examines-the-man-trapped-under-phenomenon%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20actor-director%20makes%20the%20film%20equally%20about%20his%20wife%20and%20their%20troubled%20marriage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmaestro-bradley-coopers-biopic-of-leonard-bernstein-examines-the-man-trapped-under-phenomenon%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reasons%20For%20CERT-IN's%20Exemption%20From%20RTI%20Provisions%20Are%20%E2%80%98Secret%E2%80%99%2C%20DoPT%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F12193303%2FScreen-Shot-2021-04-12-at-7.32.14-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT)%20has%20refused%20to%20disclose%20documentary%20records%20that%20exempt%20the%20Indian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20(CERT-IN)%20from%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CERT%20is%20the%20national%20nodal%20agency%20for%20responding%20to%20computer%20security%20incidents%20as%20and%20when%20they%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20information%20was%20sought%20by%20RTI%20activist%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%20following%20a%20gazette%20notification%20on%20November%2023%2C%20which%20stated%20that%20the%20second%20schedule%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20was%20amended%20to%20include%20the%20CERT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20implies%20that%20the%20CERT%20will%20be%20exempt%20from%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20except%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20information%20is%20sought%20in%20cases%20of%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20or%20human%20rights%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20RTI%20request%2C%20Nayak%20sought%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20cabinet%20note%20relating%20to%20the%20amendment%20of%20the%20second%20schedule%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%2C%20the%20note%20put%20up%20for%20the%20consideration%20of%20the%20committee%20of%20secretaries%20containing%20the%20proposal%20relating%20to%20the%20said%20amendment%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20all%20documents%20relating%20to%20the%20inter-ministerial%20consultations%20held%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20said%20amendment%20proposal%20till%20date%2C%20along%20with%20all%20file%20notings%20and%20correspondence%20held%20in%20paper%20and%20electronic%20form%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20said%20amendment%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20sought%20a%20copy%20of%20all%20official%20records%20demonstrating%20compliance%20with%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20DoPT%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20then-joint%20secretary%2C%20Devesh%20Chaturvedi%2C%20in%202015%20regarding%20the%20procedure%20for%20notifying%20new%20organisations%20under%20the%20second%20schedule%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20aforementioned%20amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENayak%E2%80%99s%20RTI%20request%20referred%20to%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20in%202015%20that%20proper%20guidelines%20be%20adopted%20to%20ensure%20wide%20public%20consultation%20prior%20to%20any%20body%20being%20exempted%20from%20the%20RTI%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20also%20recommended%20that%20prior%20to%20the%20government%20issuing%20a%20notification%20under%20Section%2024(2)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20empowers%20it%20to%20amend%20the%20second%20schedule%20%E2%80%93%20the%20name%20of%20the%20proposed%20body%2C%20the%20details%20of%20its%20functioning%20and%20an%20explanation%20on%20how%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20responds%20to%20grounds%20set%20out%20under%20Section%2024%20should%20be%20publicly%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20specified%20time-frame%20should%20be%20allowed%20for%20members%20of%20the%20public%20to%20raise%20objections%20to%20the%20proposal%2C%20the%20committee%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20also%20be%20in%20line%20with%20the%20proactive%20disclosures%20required%20under%20Sections%204(c)%20and%20(d)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20and%20the%20Pre-Legislative%20Consultation%20Policy%20(PCLP)%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20notifications%20under%20Section%2024%20by%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20must%20comprehensively%20and%20explicitly%20specify%20how%20the%20organisation%20that%20is%20being%20exempted%20fits%20into%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%9Cintelligence%20and%20security%20organisations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20reply%20on%20December%2028%2C%202023%2C%20the%20DoPT%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CSection%2024%20of%20the%20RTI%20act%20provides%20that%20nothing%20contained%20in%20this%20Act%20shall%20apply%20to%20the%20intelligence%20and%20security%20organisations%20specified%20in%20the%20second%20schedule%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20proposal%20of%20exemption%20of%20Indian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20from%20the%20ambit%20of%20RTI%20Act%20has%20been%20dealt%20in%20File%20No.%201%2F3%2F2021-IR%20II%20which%20relates%20to%20amendment%20in%20second%20schedule%20to%20the%20RTI%20Act%2C%202005.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20the%20information%20regarding%20CERT%E2%80%99s%20inclusion%20in%20the%20second%20schedule%20was%20of%20%E2%80%9Csecret%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20information%20provided%20by%20the%20organisations%20concerned%20including%20Indian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20for%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20second%20schedule%20is%20of%20secret%20nature%20and%20exempted%20under%20Section%208(1)(a)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20i.e.%20information%2C%20disclosure%20of%20which%20would%20prejudicially%20affect%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%2C%20the%20security%2C%20strategic%2C%20scientific%20or%20economic%20interests%20of%20the%20state%2C%20relation%20with%20foreign%20state%20or%20lead%20to%20incitement%20of%20an%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFurther%2C%20information%20is%20also%20exempted%20under%20Section%208(1)(i)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20being%20record%20of%20deliberations%20of%20Secretaries%20and%20other%20officers%20and%20part%20of%20the%20Note%20for%20Committee%20of%20Secretaries%20which%20itself%20is%20Secret%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%202015%20committee%20recommendations%20were%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20accepted%20by%20the%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHence%2C%20compliance%20with%20the%20said%20recommendations%20does%20not%20arise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Nayak%20said%20that%20the%20refusal%20to%20provide%20the%20documents%20is%20%E2%80%9Cintriguing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20refusal%20is%20simply%20intriguing%20because%20when%20the%20NDA%20government%20decided%20to%20include%20the%20Strategic%20Forces%20Command%20(SFC)%20under%20the%20excluded%20list%2C%20the%20CPIO%20gave%20me%20all%20the%20information%20including%20file%20noting%20and%20correspondence%20and%20the%20note%20put%20up%20to%20the%20committee%20of%20secretaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20looks%20like%20the%20Government%20is%20treating%20CERT-IN%20as%20more%20strategic%20to%20our%20security%20interests%20than%20the%20SFC%2C%20which%20looks%20after%20our%20strategic%20and%20defence%20assets%20including%20nuclear%20weapons.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704463203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F12193303%2FScreen-Shot-2021-04-12-at-7.32.14-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Finfo-on-cert-in-inclusion-rti-exempt-orgs-is-secret%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Activist%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%20had%20sought%20to%20know%20through%20an%20RTI%20filed%20in%20November%20about%20the%20deliberations%20behind%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20CERT-IN%20in%20the%20list%20of%20organisations%20that%20are%20exempt%20from%20the%20RTI%20Act's%20ambit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Finfo-on-cert-in-inclusion-rti-exempt-orgs-is-secret%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20Rs%20259%20Crore%2C%20BJP%20Received%2070%25%20of%20Donations%20by%20Electoral%20Trusts%20in%202022-23%3A%20ECI%20Data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01145249%2F406110211_773446158163006_4756603232278021214_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20received%20over%2070%25%20of%20the%20total%20donations%20by%20electoral%20trusts%20in%202022-23%2C%20according%20to%20data%20shared%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20party%20received%20Rs%20259.08%20crore%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20366%20crore%20collected%20by%20five%20electoral%20trusts%20that%20submitted%20their%20annual%20reports%20to%20the%20ECI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20highest%20corporate%20donation%20of%20Rs%2087%20crore%20came%20from%20Megha%20Engineering%20and%20Infrastructures.%20Serum%20Institute%20of%20India%20and%20ArcelorMittal%20Nippon%20Steel%20gave%20Rs%2050.25%20crore%20and%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%20political%20funding%20through%20these%20trusts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectoral%20trusts%20were%20introduced%20by%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance-II%20regime%20in%202013%20to%20facilitate%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20by%20corporations%20and%20individuals.%20However%2C%20unlike%20anonymous%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20the%20trusts%20are%20supposed%20to%20declare%20their%20donation%20reports%20to%20the%20ECI%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectoral%20trusts%20are%20required%20by%20rules%20to%20distribute%20at%20least%2095%25%20of%20their%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%20In%202022-23%2C%20however%2C%20these%20trusts%20distributed%2099.99%25%20of%20their%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022-23%2C%2013%20out%20of%20the%2018%20electoral%20trusts%2C%20registered%20with%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Direct%20Taxes%2C%20submitted%20their%20reports%20to%20the%20ECI.%20The%20reports%20show%20that%20only%20five%20trusts%20received%20donations%20from%20corporates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20366%20crore%20received%20by%20the%20five%20trusts%20from%2039%20corporates%2C%20over%2090%25%20contributions%20came%20from%2010%20business%20houses%2C%20an%20analysis%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20shows.%20Out%20of%20the%20total%20donations%2C%20Prudent%20Elec