iling%20stress%20in%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20case%20concerning%20Vidarbha%20Industries%20Power%20Ltd%20and%20Axis%20Bank%20Ltd%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20ruled%20that%20the%20existence%20of%20debt%20and%20its%20default%20does%20not%20automatically%20mean%20the%20case%20has%20to%20be%20admitted%20for%20bankruptcy%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20said%20that%20it%20was%20wrong%20on%20the%20part%20of%20NCLT%20and%20its%20appellate%20tribunal%20to%20hold%20a%20view%20that%20if%20a%20corporate%20debtor%20was%20in%20default%20of%20payment%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20option%20for%20the%20tribunal%20but%20to%20admit%20it%20for%20a%20bankruptcy%20resolution.%20This%2C%20the%20above-cited%20source%2C%20said%20it%20prompted%20the%20NCLT%20to%20admit%20more%20bankruptcy%20resolution%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704450624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04122517%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnearly-7000-companies-waiting-in-queue-for-nclt-to-admit-cases-for-bankruptcy-resolution-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Besides%20staff%20crunch%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court's%20ruling%20of%20July%202022%20is%20also%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20creditors%20for%20a%20bankruptcy%20rescue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnearly-7000-companies-waiting-in-queue-for-nclt-to-admit-cases-for-bankruptcy-resolution-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Marvel%20game%20is%20available%20at%20100%25%20discount%3A%20How%20to%20claim%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704450273000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106573880%2Cimgsize-1772096.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2F