%3EThe%20Islamist%20militant%20extremist%20group%20posted%20a%20statement%20on%20its%20affiliate%20Telegram%20channels%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%20saying%C2%A0two%20of%20its%20members%20%E2%80%9Cactivated%20their%20explosives%20vests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20bombs%20exploded%20in%20the%20Iranian%20city%20of%20Kerman%20on%20Wednesday%20(%20January%203)%20and%20killed%20scores%20gathered%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-deadly-blasts-near-grave-of-slain-qassem-soleimani%2Fa-67882464%5C%22%3Ecommemorate%20the%20death%20of%20Soleimani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20prominent%20Iranian%20general%20leader%20killed%20by%C2%A0a%20US%20drone%20strike%20in%20neighboring%20Iraq%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blast%20was%20the%20deadliest%20attack%20on%20Iranian%20soil%20in%20the%2045-year%20history%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuicide%20bombers%20reportedly%20carried%20out%20bombings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Iranian%20state%20media%20reported%C2%A0suicide%20bombers%20probably%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan-what-we-know-about-the-deadly-blasts%2Fa-67889458%5C%22%3Ecarried%20out%20the%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state-run%20IRNA%20news%20agency%20reported%20surveillance%20footage%20from%20the%20route%20to%20the%20commemoration%20at%20Kerman%E2%80%99s%20Martyrs%20Cemetery%20clearly%20showed%20a%20male%20suicide%20bomber%20detonating%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cause%20of%20the%20second%20blast%20was%20most%20likely%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20IRNA%20reported%2C%20quoting%20what%20it%20called%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinformed%20source.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoleimani%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20US%20drone%20attack%20at%20Baghdad%20airport%20in%202020.%20He%20was%20a%20high-ranking%20official%20in%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%C2%A0(IRGC)%20and%20in%20command%20of%20the%20elite%20Qud